data.description: Want a nice home on an acre with a shop?  This is it!  Versatile layout with a formal dining room that could also be an office and a large breakfast room with fireplace that could also be a hearth room!  Pretty entrance opens to the dining room and large living area featureing a double sided fireplace and tile floors that look like hardwood.  Plenty of natural sunlight making for a cheerful breakfast/hearth/kitchen area with a fabulous view of your private backyard.  You'll love the kitchen with beautiful cabinets, granite countertops, farm sink, plenty of workspace, and stainless steel appliances...including the fridge.  Peaceful and relaxing primary suite with double trey ceiings.  AND that laundry room...sink, cabinets, folding counter!  Dad will be in heaven with the fabulous 30x30 shop with garage door and electricity.  Plenty of room for those summer cookouts too!  New roof 2022 & new Heat/air 2021.  Bedroom carpet is being replaced on Jan 24th.
